  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of libgweather</title>

    <para>
      First, fix a bug in the test suite that causes problems because of a
      duplicate weather station:
    </para>

<screen><userinput remap="pre">sed -i '338a "KX26",' libgweather/test_libgweather.c</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install <application>libgweather</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

meson --prefix=/usr .. &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To test the results, issue: <command>LANG=C ninja test</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

